Answer.comments: Sorry about the one sentence I couldnt hear.  Sometimes the trains that go through town here are really loud, and that one was so loud even having over the ear headphones didnt keep him from drowning out what I was trying to listen to.
Answer.guess_accent: Somewhere in the middle east, maybe.
Answer.language_background_free: I only speak American English.  I have never studied another language or lived anywhere but here.
